There was a wicked chuckle from TARANTULUS, "Good, good, then come in
then and we shall talk."

The doors to what used to be HYDRAS' base opened to allow the
Predacons entry. As they did so they revealed the docking bay where
SCAREM and IGUANUS stood waiting.

http://tfwiki.net/w2/images2/f/fa/Scarem-packageart.jpg
http://www.tfu.info/1999/Predacon/Iguanus/robotmode.jpg

They approached DINOBOT and SKYSHADOW as they came in, "Tarantulus
wants you on the bridge." IGUANUS said without much of a preamble.

SCAREM nodded eagerly.
